<br>
Over the course of the next few months we have one main goal, as I see it: get new members without degrading the quality of our ranks.  The first things that Salt and I are doing about this is giving out more promotions to Officer, so that we have more guildies that can recruit (there is a whole other thread about this).   More devious steps will be taken in the future if this does not help <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
