<br>
I'm making a list of the current guild roster before I leave, and anyone that hasn't gone up at least one level by mid July will get a polite note saying that they are welcome back in th guild any time they like, and will get booted (if you want to do this sooner Ring, feel free).<br>
<br>
Untill I return, Ringware will be the defacto guild leader.  She is authorized to promote, demote, recruit, and boot at will.  In fact anyone of officer rank is welcome to recruit whoever they like (I trust the judgement of all the active players that we have left).  <br>
<br>
We may have more active guildies then we know, I've been on all week and have only seen two of the four I know are still playing regularly (and each of them only for a few hours).    However, I realize that the guild is pretty sparse right now, and I bear no I'll will towards anyone that decides to leave.  I'm staying in KoN 'till hell freezes (all of the guilds I was in before bit, and bit, and bit some more), but that doesn't mean you should feel you have to.  I am really greatful to those that are still with us, I hope that you are still around when I return.  And if we grew some new members, that wouldn't be a bad thing at all <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub27.ezboard.com/fknightsofnorrath91133frm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=31.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub27.ezboard.com/fknightsofnorrath91133frm2.showNextMessage?topicID=31.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub27.ezboard.com/fknightsofnorrath91133frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub27.ezboard.com/fknightsofnorrath91133frm2.emailToFriend?topicID=31.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub27.ezboard.com/fknightsofnorrath91133frm2.threadControl?topicID=31.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub27.ezboard.com/fknightsofnorrath91133frm2.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=31.topic><img src=h